                                    <desc>Apparently a later addition within the coronis and text dividers, referring to <ref target="#a3"/>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">አዝርዕተ፡ ዳግማይ፡ ዳዊት፡ እሙንቱ፡</q>
